Program: Letter from America by Alistair Cooke
Title: Loss of sportsmanship
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b0407hz0
Last Broadcast Date: Sun 3 Jul 1977
Sporting behaviour worsens as big money and TV deals takes over the major games. This archive edition of Letter from America was recorded by one of two listeners, who between them taped and labelled over 650 Letter From America programmes from 1973 to 1989. It was restored by the BBC in 2014.